My first real jailbreak map and first map. So don't hate too hard ;).

The fix includes smaller platforms so they can't run across easily. New textures outside and at soccer, clearer window in soccer, new sun color and direction, placings for obstacle course, smaller solitary door, bigger glass window for stoplights. A block between the lanes so you can't get on top of them.
Enjoy :).


It includes 14 CT spawns and 56 T spawns.

There is a chance for 2 pistols to spawn in all 16 cells (except solitary).

There is 1 vent in cells, 1 armory tele cell, and a secret armory tele outside :). There are also 2 more secrets in soccer to get a gun.

Games:

There is Roulette, 4 different colors, off and on switch with random speeds chosen, doors for each of the color cages.

Soccer has its own scoreboard and reset button, you win at 6 goals. Has seating for CTs to watch.

Obstacle course which you can turn off the floor (disabled by default) and disables the fence around it.

A race with a few hurdles and 6 lanes for 6 different spots up on the podiums with releases on the backs of them.

A new floor minigame, which you hit the left button which choses which floors will disappear and a T will have to run through it and try not to die. The button on the right resets it.

Stop lights is also included where the CTs choose a light to be displayed and the Ts follow the orders given like when it turns green, you can run, when it turns yellow/orange/amber, you can shift walk, and when it turns red, stop completely. The glows outside are the buttons for the lights.

There is a cage to put the Ts in right outside of the cells.

The LR room I have not finished yet, as it only consists of a little knife fight arena, guntoss area, and a shot for shot/no scope cage.

jb\_vortex\_dimension\_v2
==================
I made the first version of the map 2 year ago. In my opinion, it was my best map, not in "Gameplay" but with all those games i created.
Today i decided to edit it, and to add more fun ;)
I add lot of news activities, and more weapons for Ts.

The Map
==================
If you want to spend a funny time, this map is for you.
It's not a "lego" or "vipinthemix", in this map, you'll have fun in playing games. There is aswell secret and way to escape the CT's, but i hope T's will have fun.

The Different Room
==================
There is 8 different Room, with different Games:

The Ice World
------------------
In this Room, you'll have only 1 game, T's have to dodge the spike, when you change the level, there is more spike.
CT's are really safe in this area, but be carefull, there is a secret gun.

The Color World
------------------
Here you can found the 'last request' with guntoss and shot 4 shot.
In this new version, i added a new simon say, made by KNY.
There is a secret item in this room ;)

The Space World
------------------
Again, there is only 1 game. T's have to jump on the rock, and when the game start, they desappear randomly. If they fall in the "space" they die :)
Here 2 Secret guns.

The Dubstep World
------------------
Yeah, it's the DISCO ! Some people will say "no it isn't DUBSTEP !!" Ok ok, we can say "Kill the noise", but this room is really awesome in my opinion. I hope you'll enjoy it ^^

The Psychedelique World
------------------
In this one, there is a "climb-race". When CTs press the button, the wall desappear, and the 2 team have to go at the end. When 1 T press the button at the end, his team is teleported in "Winners" and the other team in "Loosers"

The Theater
------------------
You can do what you want here, there is some "ambient" song, and lot of disguise. When you press on the Game, a random light will be turned off (like a couch room).

The Minecraft World
------------------
Maybe the biggest room, into this one, there is a Swimming Pool, a little game with pigs (your imagination have to invent the rules :P) and the game in the cave. Here you have to put 1 T with the enderman, and all the other one in the left. The player with the enderman will have to catch his friends, to kill them. In this area is the only real "vent". At the end on the vent, shoot the screen to be teleported ;)

2nd Space Game
------------------
It's a race, with 4 winners.
Welcome in the galaxy !


To end
==================
There is a lot of other funny item / secret/ sound, your work to find them ;).
Sorry for my bad english, and i hope you'll have fun in my map.

v1_2
==================

- Nerf disco (causing lag)
- Simon fixed
- Ice World : more dmg

VipintheMix V1.2 [RELEASED] It's my very first jailmap. Based on Electric_VIP but fully remastered.

Map features:
  • Soccer
  • Speedrunway
  • LR-Room
  • Guntoss
  • Knifefight
  • Race
  • Pool
  • Diving spots
  • Slide tube
  • Vipcel
  • Disco
  • Minipool
  • Bar
  • Yard
  • Jumpcontest
  • Basketball
  • Bunnyhop
  • Skate
  • Throw contest
  • Dodgeball
  • Bigjail
  • Loads of secrets! 

Video with all the secrets

Songs used:

  •  Deadmau5 - Ghosts 'n Stuff
  •  Deadmau5 - Strobe 
  • Afrojack - Take over Control 
  • Martin Solveig - Hello
  •  David Guetta / Rihanna - Who's that chick  
  • Showtek - We Speak Music

Explanation Games 

  1. Diving Spots - The point of diving is diving into the colored 'baths'. When you are at green you should jump in green. 
  2. Dodgeball - Take place in the red/blue chambers. Someone press the start button above and dodgeball will start. 
  3. Speed-runway - Just a runway around soccer. Just for the bored CTs. 
  4. Xtreme Guntoss - Run over the push_trigger and fly around the corner with a curve. Throw your gun as far as possible. Just like regular guntoss. 
  5. Throw contest - Only 1 v 1 person at a time. When you are with 2 in 1 chamber it won't work! Once it starts throw the nades into the green holes. It is camp proof. You will die after 60 seconds. Wait a few seconds before the next run. It doesn't work all the time. 70% it does. 30% doesn't.


Suggested plugins and settings are:

  • phys_pushscale 900
  • sv_airaccelerate 100 (or higher)
  • Nosmoke plugins (sourcemod or eventscripts (see 4 and 5))
  •  No-smoke plugin for dodgeball: downloadable here

For questions contact me at steam.
Dutchkiller

This map is a port from CSGO. The map was created by thorgot the creator of jb_avalanche and jb_airship 2 great maps which are in counter strike source already ;). This map is based on Undertale, a game by Toby Fox.

In this port, I had to take out/replace a few minigames and secrets due to limitations in hammer compared to CSGO.

Still, this map comes with a great list of features which include :

Minigames in cells
Decathlon  
Strafe Jump: easy, medium, and hard; 0, 5, or 10 damage 
Slide Race: 4 different courses
Dodge Course: Dodge obstacles on a moving platform 
Surf: easy, medium, and hard; 0, 5, or 10 damage; recall and gate buttons 
Risky Ralph's Roulette (the CT pressing the button also has a chance of dying) 
Extreme Jumprope (Jumprope combined with 4 colors) 
9 Colors with 4 brand new events (19 total) 
Soccer
Spleef 
Easy Climb, Medium Climb, and Hard Climb 
Disco (with Undertale music) 
25 key piano that can be played. 
Secrets and vents.

An sG community map created by thorgot.
Additional textures and brushwork by Prussia.
Music remixes/covers by RichaadEB, ToxicxEternity, and theultimateonejpsx.
Models by Humin, RED_EYE, Brewster T. Koopa, and Yok99102.
